necessar y. Real pr ogress gr ows not fr om aut omatic loyalty t o majority norms, but fr om critical pr obing and the ner ve to challenge what feels
comfor table.', '["By banning sensitive debates","By summarizing facts through visuals","By creating curated echo chambers","By allowing hidden identities"]'::jsonb, 2, 'The correct option is (c).
Context from the passage : The passage clearly states that digital platforms intensify conformity because algorithms construct personalized
